import React from 'react'
import {HeaderContainer,LeftSide, MidSide, RightSide, LogoContainer, LogoImage,Option } from "./header.styles";
import Logo from "../../assets/img/logo.png"
import {CustomLink} from "../custom-link/custom-link.component";
const Header = () => {
  return (
    <HeaderContainer>
      <LeftSide>
        <LogoContainer>
          <LogoImage src={Logo}/>
        </LogoContainer>
      </LeftSide>
      <MidSide>
      <Option>
          <CustomLink to="/"/>
        </Option>
        <Option>
          <CustomLink to="/shop"/>
        </Option>
        <Option>
          <CustomLink to="/pages"/>
        </Option>
        <Option>
          <CustomLink to="/blog"/>
        </Option>
        <Option>
          <CustomLink to="/contact"/>
        </Option>
      </MidSide>
      <RightSide>
        right
      </RightSide>
    </HeaderContainer>
  )
}

export default Header
